headline: GE HealthCare Technologies (NasdaqGS:GEHC) Partners With Probo Medical Amid 4% Dip
summary: GE HealthCare Technologies (NasdaqGS:GEHC) saw its stock price rise by 2% over the last quarter. This gain coincides with the company's announcement of a distribution partnership with Probo Medical for its ultrasound machines, an event that has likely influenced investor sentiment positively. Concurrently, GEHC's strong financial performance, reflected in its fourth-quarter earnings report showing revenue and net income growth, likely supported this trend.
